invalid type: string "**Yes, I can!** I have the **`search_web`** function available.\n\nHere's what it does:\n\n### **search_web**\n- **Description**: Search the web using SearXNG (self-hosted) with DuckDuckGo as fallback. No API key required.\n- **Parameters**:\n  - `query` (string, required): The search query\n  - `n_results` (integer, optional): Number of results to return (default 5, max 20)˙